---
// WhyUs.astro
---

<section class="whyus" id="why-us">
  <div class="whyus__inner">
    <div class="whyus__left">
      <h2 class="whyus__heading">Why VAC Global Solutions?</h2>
      <p class="whyus__subtext">
        We don’t rely on assumptions. We build structured systems that bring clarity, control, and measurable execution across operations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="whyus__cards">
      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined why-card__icon">verified</span>
        <h4 class="why-card__title">Structured Execution</h4>
        <p class="why-card__text">
          Every process is mapped, defined, and controlled using PPCX-based execution frameworks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined why-card__icon">hub</span>
        <h4 class="why-card__title">Integrated Systems</h4>
        <p class="why-card__text">
          Seamless integration of production, data, and workflows through MES and ERP ecosystems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-card">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined why-card__icon">trending_up</span>
        <h4 class="why-card__title">Data-Driven Decisions</h4>
        <p class="why-card__text">
          Real-time insights and analytics that drive performance, efficiency, and continuous improvement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .whyus {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: var(--color-surface-container-low);
  }

  .whyus__inner {
    max-width: 80rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .whyus__left {
    max-width: 28rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .whyus__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .whyus__subtext {
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .whyus__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .why-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(25, 28, 29, 0.02);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }

  .why-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(25, 28, 29, 0.06);
  }

  .why-card__icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .why-card__title {
    font-family: var(--font-headline);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-on-surface);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .why-card__text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .whyus__inner {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .whyus__left {
      text-align: left;
      flex: 0 0 33%;
    }

    .whyus__cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>